I didn't look to see who she was, thinking it was just some posh old English woman they got for the promo and I studied every inch of Leela's outfit, the shading, the color, lighting, when it changed, when she wore something different, I adored this woman so much and didn't recognize her until the very end when she said, "I still got it" I gasped! LEELA!

Now I'm ashamed of myself that I didn't recognize her and now wonder what it was in that final bit with her that I suddenly realized who she was?
God, how I loved that woman!
